Usage: reportSeedConnection [-help] [-constraints <seedFile>]
                            [-excNetFile <exclNetFile>] [-file <outFile>]

-help                            # Prints out the command usage
-constraints <seedFile>          # name of the input seed file
                                 # (string, optional)
-excNetFile <exclNetFile>        # name of the input excluding net file
                                 # (string, optional)
-file <outFile>                  # name of the output seed connection report
                                 # file (string, optional)